      • setCommitQueueTag

        public void setCommitQueueTag(String tag)
        Set commit-queue tag. Implicitly enabled commit-queue commit.
        Parameters:
        tag - User defined opaque tag attached to the resulting queue item if using the Maapi.COMMIT_NCS_COMMIT_QUEUE_ASYNC or Maapi.COMMIT_NCS_COMMIT_QUEUE_SYNC flag. The tag is present in all notifications and events sent referencing the queue item.
